node.text:
How cute? 🙈 Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on worlderlust.com (link in my bio: @worlderlust)

Animals never forget those who love and care for them - no matter how much time may pass 🙏🏼💚@zwfmiami @limbanizwf @mariowildlife @misstyflower

You guys know how big of a believer I am in the human/animal bond. I believe that this planet was meant for us all. I hate seeing animals being poached and habitats being destroyed through human greed. Somewhere along the line, we as humans, have stopped caring for wildlife. We started placing ourselves first, forgetting about the planet and animals in the process. Videos like this prove otherwise. They show the connection between humans who place animals first and the love that is possible. They show that we are meant to coexist, and I hope they cause people to rethink the value and importance that we place on the planet and animals that we share it with. Earth is meant for us all 🌎🌍🌏🙌🏼💪🏼

📽 @gabaaa_31 via @maxstrong

Would you dive in these @nature places? 🤿 We can post your pictures in our account. Check the link in our bio for more info: @worlderlust (worlderlust.com)

Which one is your favourite? 1-5?⁣⁣⁣

1 - The P31 from Comino in Malta
2&3 - Aqaba military museum in Jordan
4 - the Giannis D at Abu Nuhas, Red Sea
5 - The wreck of Tyrifjord near Askvoll, Norway 
📸 @alex_dawson_photography

node.text:
Hotel pool views in the Swiss Alps 🇨🇭 Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on worlderlust.com (link in my bio: @worlderlust)

It really doesn’t get any better than this, don't you think? 🤩

Settled in the municipality of Ennetbürgen in the canton of Nidwalden in Switzerland. With a 34ºC heated outdoor pool, incredible views of Lake Lucerne, a place for slow down and contemplation, this is just one of the many gems that Switzerland has to offer making you fall in love with the country. 😍

📽 @ryanresatka
📍 Switzerland
🎶 Powfu, beabadoobee - death bed (coffee for your head)
